B.Fx=s(["Quetzal to Auburn Valley.","Go to bank and take out your cup of tea, drink it.","Buy Steel Axe + Mithril Axe from Axe shop.","Cut TWO dead trees (some NE and some by the scenery), convert both to planks.","Buy Air Staff + Fire Staff from staff shop, equip one."],t.s)
B.nB=s(["text","multiline","number","phone","datetime","emailAddress","url","visiblePassword","name","address","none","webSearch","twitter"],t.s)
B.Fz=s(["Bring: weapon + alch runes + knife + mithril axe + box traps + bird snares.","IF Tier 3 + Map relic, use Map to teleport directly to birds.","Otherwise: quetzal to Tal Teklan \u2192 run NE to Crimson Swifts.","Home tele and quetzal back to run east to Tropical Wagtails while cutting trees for 5 WC.","Quetzal to Hunter Guild \u2192 catch Jerboas SE until 53 Hunter.","Buy box traps + knife from General Store before hunting red chins later.","Plant guam seeds (from hunter) and acorn at 15 Farming in Auburn Valley anytime."],t.s)
B.FV=s([4,9,14,19],t.t)
B.G2=s(["At 57 Hunter: do Gilman \u2192 Cervus \u2192 Ornus contracts until 72.","At 72+: set up block list. Do EXPERT rumours only.","Lots of high-value content at 72+: Tecu Salamanders, Moonlight Moth, Red Chins, Antelopes.","Catch 500 chinchompas naturally during hunting activities."],t.s)
