B.G9=s(["TRANSMUTE RELIC: Take bones from hunter + slayer, note them, transmute to dagannoth bones.","Bury until 30 Prayer. Stop 1 at dragon bones and bury [30]. Stop 1 at wyrm and bury by wyrm skeleton on agility course [30].",'Buy jugs of wine from Aldarin wine shop (west of bank). Use "Rest" at Varlamore prayer training method.',"After overheads: complete Meat and Greet quest (map brings you to direwolf step).","Sunset Coast fishing shop: cook tuna + swordfish (raw fish available there or transmute).","Transmute any gem to red topaz and cut it.","Hunter guild log method: bank 4 full inventories of logs and transmute the following fletching tasks.","Transmute some blood runes \u2192 cast a Wave spell (level 65+ magic required)."],t.s)
B.Ga=s(["Pick up bones constantly to train Prayer.","High Alch any rune items you find to fund supplies.","Complete quests in Civitas and unlock POH before combat."],t.s)
B.Gb=s(["Complete the Heart of Darkness for Amoxliatl access.","Frost Crabs and Amoxliatl are in the Civitas cave system.","Fully decorating all three Auburn Valley totems is a key task batch.","The Medium Karamja Diary requires completing multiple steps.","Equip the Fire Cape last \u2014 this marks the end of the route."],t.s)
