B.GJ=s(["!! Optional: Talk to spice merchant in Bazaar (option 2), open box with code 2546 (Meat and Greet start).","West bank: take out bucket + steel pickaxe + use bones from imp on Molossus (dog).","Run NW of Civitas to kill thief then use secret passage.","Buy Bronze Plate + Legs from armour shop after unlocking Karamja (for Equip Full Bronze Set task).","Thieve cake stalls until 34 Thieving before going to Aldarin for Death on the Isle.","Pottery oven: take clay from bank, add water on the way, use on pottery wheel then pottery oven SE Civitas.","Orbs: do trips with 13\xd7 bucket of sand + soda ash from charter to furnace; blow unpowered orbs on way back to charter until 100 done."],t.s)
