B.Hv=s(["Tier 3 by now \u2014 use Map relic tele to Cam Torum, otherwise quetzal and run.","Buy all pickaxes from mithril \u2192 rune. Buy TWO mith pickaxes and TWO rune pickaxes.",'Alch 1 mithril pickaxe for "Convert item 500+ coins" task.',"Sacrifice 1 rune pickaxe at Death's domain later.","Hunter Guild dark cave (west side): collect logs \u2192 cut arrow shafts \u2192 bank oak logs for oak shortbow.","POH construction order: 2 normal planks \u2192 chair (5 con) \u2192 oak crafting table 1 (20 con) \u2192 hoop & stick \u2192 oak larder \u2192 jester (29 con) \u2192 redecorate.","Red chins in Kastori (Map tele) to 73 Hunter.","Catch black warlock butterfly near chins."],t.s)
