B.Hx=s(["Complete the Civitas early tasks and reach the hunter area.","Focus on skilling tasks to hit Total Level 250.","Pick up flax and spin wool whenever you pass near Auburn Valley."],t.s)
B.Hy=s(["Rowboat to Tal Teklan. Buy from rune shop: 5 elemental packs, 5 mind, 5 cosmics, 75 natures, 1 chaos, 1 death.","Low alch anything for mage XP.","Ranged shop: buy 10 iron arrows + shortbow.","Run east out of Tal Teklan to kill frog near Doom dungeon shortcut.","EH/Woodsman: catch 8 Crimson Swifts, then 15 Tropical Wagtails. Others can skip.","Rowboat to Kastori. Fishing shop: small net, fishing rod, fly rod, harpoon, lobster pot, 50 bait, sardines."],t.s)
B.Hz=s(["These tasks can be done at any point after Death on the Isle (or later if preferred).","Thieving: wealthy citizens for 28 pouches \u2192 house keys for 25 valuables.","Mining: Stonecutter Outpost east of Cam Torum for most tasks.","Calcified deposits south of Cam Torum."],t.s)
B.HA=s(["Take boat to Sunset Coast. Helmet shop: buy bronze and addy full helms.","Fishing shop: buy 50 tuna, 100 swordfish raw fish for cooking tasks.","Run north to Cam Torum: buy herblore supplies, pickaxes (steel, mith, addy, rune), 50 law runes, 500 natures.","Stonecutter Outpost (east of Cam Torum): mine 1 clay, 50 iron, 20 silver, 2 coal, 3 gold, 50 mithril ore.","Run east to coast: big net fish for 20 mackerel, 10 cod.","Make: 1 bronze bar, 15 iron bars \u2192 smith 150 iron arrowtips \u2192 fletch 150 iron arrows.","Smelt 20 silver bars \u2192 make 20 silver tiaras."],t.s)
