B.HJ=s(["Quetzal to Aubernvale (top left). Drink the cup of tea immediately.","EH/Woodsman: toggle auto-bank on. Chop dead tree near river first.","Buy: Steel, Mithril, Adamant Axe from Axe shop. Air and Fire Staff from staff shop.","Forestry Kit from Forestry shop southwest of Nemus Retreat \u2014 equip it for Forestry events.","Vale Totems miniquest: bring 5 oak, 5 willow, 5 maple logs."],t.s)
B.HK=s(["Quetzal to Tal Teklan.","Buy: shortbow + 10 iron arrows + iron/steel knives. Purple Dye from dye shop.","Rune shop: buy 1 of each elemental pack + 1 mind pack + 50 chaos. Spend ALL remaining gold on nature runes.","Kill chickens with MACE (not knives/bow) for the 5-creature-with-mace task.","After this section: UNLOCK TIER 2 and choose WOODSMAN relic.","Boat to Kastori. Buy fishing supplies: 1k feathers, 1 bait pack, lobster pot, harpoon, fishing rod, fly rod, big fishing net."],t.s)
